Kate Toncray https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kate_Toncray 0 Kate Toncray (1867 – December 6, 1927) was an American actress of the silent era. She appeared in 178 films between 1905 and 1925. She was born in St. Louis, Missouri and died in Manhattan, New York City. Kate_Toncray ( 1867 – December_6_,_1927 ) was an_American_actress of the_silent_era .
